   MT=2   Angular distributions of secondary neutrons given for   2837 1451
     elastic scattering are from ENDF/B-V.                        2837 1451
          If desired, angular distributions can be calculated by  2837 1451
     the user on a finer energy grid from the R-Matrix resonance  2837 1451
     parameters in File 2, MT=151.                                2837 1451
