   MT=16  (n,2n) reaction; includes simple constant yields for    2837 1451
      the neutron and 61Ni residual, and energy dependent yield   2837 1451
      based on TNG calculated gamma-ray spectra for the gamma ray;2837 1451
      TNG calculated normalized distributions are given for each  2837 1451
