      yield based on TNG calculated gamma-ray spectra for the     2837 1451
      gamma ray; calculated normalized distributions are given    2837 1451
      for each product.  Isotropy is assumed.                     2837 1451
   MT=51 through 54 Inelastic scattering exciting levels;         2837 1451
      assumed isotropic.                                          2837 1451
   MT=91  Inelastic scattering exciting the continuum; includes   2837 1451
      simple constant yields for the neutron and 62Ni residual    2837 1451
      and energy dependent yield based on TNG calculated gamma-   2837 1451
      ray spectra for the gamma ray; TNG calculated normalized    2837 1451
      distributions are given for each.  Isotropy is assumed.     2837 1451
   MT=103 (n,p) reaction; includes simple constant yields for     2837 1451
      proton and 62Co residual, and energy dependent yield based  2837 1451
      on calculated gamma-ray spectra for gamma ray; calculated   2837 1451
      normalized distributions are given for each product.        2837 1451
      Isotropy is assumed.                                        2837 1451
   MT=107 (n,a) reaction; includes simple constant yields for     2837 1451
      alpha and 59Fe residual, and energy dependent yield based   2837 1451
      on calculated gamma-ray spectra for gamma ray; calculated   2837 1451
      calculated normalized distributions are given for each      2837 1451
      product.  Isotropy is assumed.                              2837 1451
